		<node id="editorData">
			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. Use Debug Book - Set Quest Flags - Act 2 - GLO - Lifting the curse - Quest States  - Halsin at camp with Spirit&#xD;&#xA;2. Use Debug Book - Set Quest Flags - Act 2 - GLO - Lifting the curse - Quest States - Oliver Fled to Town - teleports Oliver to the plaza in the Town and readies him for a fight. Also teleports you to the plaza as well, you'll only need to approach Oliver to start combat.&#xD;&#xA;3. Kill Plush." />
